00074 int Option_VDF::test_mot(const Motcle& motlu) const
00075 {
00076   Motcles les_mots(2);
00077   {
00078     les_mots[1] = "oui";
00079     les_mots[0] = "non";
00080   }
00081 
00082   int rang=les_mots.search(motlu);
00083   if (rang==-1)
00084     {
00085       Cerr<<"Method "<<que_suis_je()<<"::test_mot : Tested keyword is "<<motlu<<finl;
00086       Cerr<<"One expected a keyword among yhe following :"<<finl<<les_mots<<finl;
00087       abort();
00088       return -1;
00089     }
00090   else
00091     return rang;
00092 }

00117 int Option_VDF::lire_motcle_non_standard(const Motcle& mot, Entree& is)
00118 {
00119   Motcle motlu;
00120   if (mot=="traitement_coins")
00121     {
00122       is >>motlu;
00123       if (test_mot(motlu))
00124         {
00125           Cerr<< motlu <<" will affect the action of the method Zone_Cl_VDF::completer"<<finl;
00126           Option_VDF::traitement_coins=1;
00127         }
00128       else
00129         Option_VDF::traitement_coins=0;
00130       return 1;
00131     }
00132   else if (mot=="P_imposee_aux_faces")
00133     {
00134       is >>motlu;
00135       if (test_mot(motlu))
00136         {
00137           Cerr<<motlu<<" will affect the action of the operator gradient for Neumann_sortie_libre boundary condition" <<finl;
00138           Cerr<<motlu<<" and therefore the assembleur action will also be affected."<<finl;
00139           Option_VDF::coeff_P_neumann=2.;
00140         }
00141       else
00142         Option_VDF::coeff_P_neumann=1.;
00143       return 1;
00144     }
00145   else
00146     {
00147       Cerr << mot << "is not a keyword understood by " << que_suis_je() << "in methode lire_motcle_non_standard"<< finl;
00148       exit();
00149     }
00150   return -1;
00151 }
